{
  "stem": "11089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What bothered me so terribly-- when I went out in the city in Chust to buy products, I saw trucks loaded with Hungarian and German soldiers escaping from the battle field, which was 80 kilometers in a place called, [?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yassina. ?] It was a border between Galicia and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If the Russians would have moved five, six hours, they would have captured us and we would have stayed home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for some political reasons, they stopped at the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And during those few weeks, till they started to move on, Eichmann succeeded to take away 250,000 Jews from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If they would have moved-- I saw them only wounded, running away from the battlefield.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They stopped at the border, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were just 80 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And nothing-- they didn't move for some reasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was supervised by [INAUDIBLE] Gendarmerie.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They-- they supervised it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The conditions were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very, very poor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us, I remember-- I speak about my own case, my family-- they put us into one room, maybe 10 feet long and maybe 12 wide.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were four families there on one floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had one corner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody had one corner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's how we lived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we started to sew-- to make our stars, to be ready to go to the train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we still had food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had some food brought with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were allowed, like I said, to bring in some-- the Jewish-- the Jewish committee gave the money to buy some food for the people.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
